text: May El Calamawy (, ; born October 28, 1986) is an Egyptian-Palestinian actress. She has worked and lived in the United States since 2015. She is known for her roles in the American television series Ramy as Dena Hassan and Moon Knight as Layla El-Faouly. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Bahraini people Category:Egyptian movie actors Category:Egyptian television actors Category:Palestinian people
